projects.description:
Worked across a range of products to accelerate David Lloyd's digital transformation roadmap. Their plan was split across workstreams to increase new memebership, improve retention, increase sales & subscriptions (e.g. to classes and courses) and streamline their internal processes to improve efficiency.

My role included work to:
* Upgrade their public facing website to increase membership sign-ups by providing a modern design and customisable content via a custom-made Content Management System;
* Upgrade their internal booking system to automate manual processes and improving the code base by extracting an old PHP monolith into Java microservices;
* Create a new membership registration app for in-club sales teams to improve the registration process and experience for both staff and prospective members.
